Midwives as Expert Witnesses

The topic modeling tool is less than zesty. It probably works better with larger data samples that have more variation in their subject matter and text characters. The topics that occurred in my corpus were all very similar and expected regardless of how little or many topics that I asked for.

March 9, 2021

This data set uses Old Bailey Proceedings to investigate how female medical practitioners understood the body. What knowledge did they use to impact criminal proceedings in the name of the crown? What medical misconceptions did they perpetuate or challenge?
